<div id = "aboutus" class = "tab-pane fade">
	<div class = "alert alert-success"><center><h3>VISION</h3></center></div>
	<h4 style="text-align: center;">Camara Education envisions a world where every learner has access to quality education and the opportunity to reach their full potential.</h4>
	<br />
	<div class = "alert alert-success"><center><h3>MISSION</h3></center></div>
	<h4 style="text-align: center;">Camara Education's mission is to use technology to improve education and provide opportunities for disadvantaged communities.<br> They work towards achieving this mission through the following objectives:</h4>
	<div class = "alert alert-success"><center><h3>OBJECTIVE</h3></center></div>
	<ol>
      <h3>Enhancing Education Access</h3>
      <p>Camara Education aims to increase access to quality education by providing schools and educational institutions in underserved areas with refurbished computers, educational software, and digital learning resources. By bridging the digital divide, they strive to ensure that all students have access to the tools and resources they need to succeed academically.</p>
      <h3>Empowering Teachers</h3>
      <p>The organization focuses on empowering teachers with the necessary skills to effectively use technology in the classroom. They provide training programs and professional development opportunities that equip educators with the knowledge and tools to integrate technology into their teaching practices, enhancing their ability to engage students and deliver quality education.</p>
      <h3>Fostering Digital Literacy</h3>
      <p>Camara Education recognizes the importance of digital literacy in today's world. They work towards fostering digital literacy skills among students, enabling them to navigate the digital landscape, leverage technology for learning, and develop critical thinking and problem-solving abilities. By equipping students with these skills, Camara Education aims to enhance their educational and career opportunities.</p>
      <h3>Promoting Sustainable Impact</h3>
      <p>The organization is committed to environmental sustainability and responsible practices. They focus on collecting, refurbishing, and repurposing used electronic devices, reducing electronic waste and its impact on the environment. Additionally, Camara Education emphasizes the importance of sustainability in their educational programs, encouraging students to become responsible digital citizens and promoting energy-efficient technology solutions.</p>
      <h3>Collaborating with Partners</h3>
      <p>Camara Education recognizes the value of partnerships and collaborations. They work with governments, schools, NGOs, and other stakeholders to implement their programs effectively and scale their impact. By collaborating with various organizations and individuals, they aim to create a collective effort towards improving education worldwide.</p>
   
	</ol>
</div>